data.description: This beautiful and remodeled home is turnkey and ready to move in.    Investors -- You will love the cash flow upside with this property.  Updated Roof, AC, Exterior Paint, Patio, Garage, Driveway, Fence, Sprinkler System, Lighting, Flooring, Kitchen, and much more.  You will enjoy entertaining your guests with this large saltwater pool and patio as well as yard space for your pets.  Save money with No HOA, in a nice mature community. Smart home comes a split floor plan, and kitchen has a large island with granite countertops. Home features an extended driveway with room for a small boat or jet ski.  *All information is intended to be accurate but is not guaranteed.
